contentrichtext.text: {{wikt|LNA}} '''LNA''' is a [[three letter acronym]] that may stand for: == Electronics/Telecom == * [[Low noise amplifier]] * [[Launch numerical aperture]] * [[Local network adapter]] * [[Local network attachment]] * [[Logistics net assessment]] == Biology == * [[Linolenic acid]] * [[Locked nucleic acid]] * [[Lung nodule assessment]] == Organization/Place == * [[Citroën LNA|LNA]], a [[Citroën]] car * [[Lantana Airport]] ([[Florida]]) == Profession == * [[Licensed nursing assistant]] == Trade == * Licencias No Automáticas previas de importación, Argentinian non-automatic [[import license]], prior to importation == Music == * [[Late Night Alumni]], a US [[House music|house]] group {{disambig}}
